OL,3,CCash spending limits for Guernsey's
OL,4,Ccommittees to combat #2 million deficit
OL,6,FGuernsey's deputy Chief Minister has
OL,7,Fannounced that the States of
OL,8,FGuernsey's committees will be given
OL,9,Fset cash spending limits next year.
OL,11,FIn a statement delivered at the States
OL,12,FAssembly this morning, Deputy Gavin St
OL,13,FPier outlined the island's financial
OL,14,Fposition as the government heads
OL,15,Ftowards the end of 2025.
OL,17,FHe revealed the Policy & Resources
OL,18,FCommittee (P&R) is currently
OL,19,Festimating an operating deficit for
OL,20,F2025 of roughly #2 million.
