OL,6,FFurther, the Corporate Services
OL,7,Fdepartment has seen high costs this
OL,8,Fyear - resulting from insurance and
OL,9,Fthe delivery of a new IT and digital
OL,10,Fmodel - creating an estimated
OL,11,Foverspend of #1.6 million.
OL,13,FThe deputy Chief Minister also
OL,14,Facknowledged ongoing issues with the
OL,15,Fisland's Revenue Service - stating
OL,16,F"the current rate of issuing
OL,17,Frepayments is not an acceptable level
OL,18,Fof service to the public".
