OL,3,CCash spending limits for Guernsey's
OL,4,Ccommittees to combat #2 million deficit
OL,6,FThe scheme taxes companies with a
OL,7,Fturnover of more than E730 million at
OL,8,F15%.
OL,10,FHowever, Deputy St Pier was clear that
OL,11,Fany estimates of these revenues are
OL,12,Fjust that, because "not a penny of
OL,13,Fthis tax has been banked to date and
OL,14,Fwill not be until 2027".
OL,16,FSome pressures may also be alleviated
OL,17,Fby document duty - the tax paid on
OL,18,Fpurchased properties - with local
OL,19,Fmarket transactions up 31% this year
OL,20,Fas compared to last.
