OL,4,Ccommittees to combat #2 million deficit
OL,6,FDeputy St Pier also promised the
OL,7,Fbudget will outline "initiatives to
OL,8,Fdeliver savings in 2026 as well as a
OL,9,Ffresh, much-needed look at our whole
OL,10,Fexpenditure".
OL,12,FHowever, he was clear that P&R must
OL,13,Fstill "raise revenues where we can
OL,14,Ffind scope - and frankly, the scope is
OL,15,Fextremely limited".
OL,17,F"We have no choice but to fund
OL,18,Fessential public services, and some of
OL,19,Fthe pressures I have spoken about
OL,20,Ftoday are already being spent, so
OL,21,Fcannot be avoided."
